FROM centos:7

RUN curl -f -L https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/g/ansible-service-broker/ansible-service-broker-latest/repo/epel-7/group_ansible-service-broker-ansible-service-broker-latest-epel-7.repo -o /etc/yum.repos.d/asb.repo
RUN yum -y install epel-release centos-release-openshift-origin \
 && yum -y install apb-container-scripts sudo origin-clients \
 && yum clean all && rm -rf /var/cache/yum

WORKDIR /mnt

RUN echo "ALL ALL=NOPASSWD: ALL" > /etc/sudoers.d/usermod

ENTRYPOINT ["apb-wrapper"]
CMD ["-h"]

LABEL RUN docker run --privileged -it --rm -v \${PWD}:/mnt -v \$HOME/.kube:/.kube -v \$HOME/.apb:/.apb -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -u \${SUDO_UID} \${IMAGE}
